content:
Efficiently Capture Complete Interaction Notes by Using a Guided Flow.

Caseworkers can use a single guided flow to easily capture meeting notes. Use the flow to write detailed notes, record attendees, document the date and time, add tags, and upload supporting documents. They can also share their notes with other users, and publish the approved notes to prevent any further edits. This efficient, unified workflow saves caseworkers from going to multiple pages to manage written and verbal communications.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience where Interaction Summary and Enhanced Interaction Note Interface are enabled.

Who: To use this feature, users need the Industries Interaction Summary permission set license.
title: Efficiently Capture Complete Interaction Notes with Guided Flow
